data.description: Welcome to this beautiful - unique custom home just minutes to I-25!  Close to both Albuquerque and Santa Fe. VIEWS! Gourmet kitchen with granite counters. The bathrooms have been updated including a jetted tub in the guest bath and large walk-in showers in the master and the downstairs guest bath.  Downstairs is a family room perfect for a pool table or movie screen, with a wet bar and a guest bedroom and bath. Inground pool was added in recent years along with a hot tub.  Placitas is quiet and has the most beautiful starry night sky's due to low light pollution. Attached 3 car-garage & detached 2 car-garage - possibly convert it into a guest house! Trees were just trimmed to show VIEWS! New carpet in master, brick floors refinished. New interior paint.
